</script></div></div><div class="clear"></div>
<p><span></span></p>
<p>This vision also indicates gaining a prestigious position and great respect among people.<br/>Seeing a poplar tree in the dream of an unmarried person, whether a girl or a young man, is an indication of an imminent marriage or engagement, or a discovery of a suitable lover.</p>
<p>The Houris in a dream indicate that the dreamer will obtain a lot of money from a lawful source, and this vision also indicates that the dreamer will obtain money through inheritance.<br/><strong>Sitting with the Houris in a dream</strong> indicates happiness and long life, and indicates that God will grant you Paradise.</p>
<p>Whoever sees the Houris in a dream and is going through problems or hardships of any kind, it means the arrival of relief, the end of these problems, and finding solutions to this difficulty.</p><div class="angwp_84394 _ning_cont _ning_hidden _ning_outer _align_center responsive" data-aid="0" data-bid="84394" data-size="custom" style="max-width:100%; width:100%;height:inherit;"><div class="_ning_label _left" style=""></div><div class="_ning_inner" style=""><script type="text/javascript">
