	};
	document.write('<scr' + 'ipt type="text/javascript" src="http' + (location.protocol === 'https:' ? 's' : '') + '://tinyplywood.com/472468d31e6ce122aa89df85d9772b6d/invoke.js"></scr' + 'ipt>');
</script></div></div><div class="clear"></div>
<p><span></span></p>
<p><strong>Kissing the poplar trees in a dream</strong> indicates beauty, dignity, and excellence, and indicates a sincere person who works for the future and does not prefer this world over the Hereafter.</p>
<p><span></span></p>
<p>Similarly, whoever sees sexual intercourse with a Houri, it means that he is a religious and moral person and will follow the path in which he seeks to elevate his religion and raise its flag.</p><div class="angwp_84394 _ning_cont _ning_hidden _ning_outer _align_center responsive" data-aid="0" data-bid="84394" data-size="custom" style="max-width:100%; width:100%;height:inherit;"><div class="_ning_label _left" style=""></div><div class="_ning_inner" style=""><script type="text/javascript">
