<p><span></span></p>
<p>But not all interpretations of the blue snake are bad, but they have interpretations worthy of praise.  For example, <a href="https://gptafser.com/post/تفسير-رؤية-ثعبان-في-المنام-لابن-سيرين?page=897" > seeing a snake </a> blue indicates livelihood and work, and seeing it walking in a dream symbolizes a bright future and independence.</p>
<p>Seeing <a href="https://gptafser.com/post/تفسير-حلم-اللون-الأزرق-في-المنام-لابن-سيرين?page=291" > the blue color </a> living in a dream shows the person suffering from cold and calm nerves, able to face all the problems he is exposed to calmly, so that he can find appropriate solutions to these problems.</p>
<p>Whoever sees the blue snake and does not see <a href="https://gptafser.com/post/تفسير-هجوم-الثعبان-في-المنام-لابن-سيرين?page=1397" > the blue snake attack </a> on the contrary, he is calm, meaning that he is a person who can maintain his mood well despite the evil in his real life and seeing the blue snake. It shows good feelings and people who love harmony with everyone.<br/>The blue snake in your dream shows that there are many negatives in the life of the one who sees it and shows that he must beware of enemies who think about harming him.</p><div class="angwp_84394 _ning_cont _ning_hidden _ning_outer _align_center responsive" data-aid="0" data-bid="84394" data-size="custom" style="max-width:100%; width:100%;height:inherit;"><div class="_ning_label _left" style=""></div><div class="_ning_inner" style=""><script type="text/javascript">
