</script></div></div><div class="clear"></div>
<p><span></span></p>
<p>Whoever saw the blue snake in his dream, this vision is not worthy of praise, because it shows the devil and shows the unbeliever, and seeing it indicates the arrival of evil.<br/>And whoever sees the blue snake fighting with him in a dream, this indicates a fight against enemies, and if he is able to do so <strong>kill the blue snake in a dream</strong> this means that you will be able to achieve victory over the enemy.<br/><a href="https://gptafser.com/post/تفسير-حلم-لدغة-ثعبان-في-المنام-لابن-سيرين?page=3881" > A blue snake bite </a> in a dream indicates exposure to trouble and <strong>eating the flesh of the blue snake in a dream</strong> indicates getting money from enemies.<br/>In the case of <a href="https://gptafser.com/post/تفسير-رؤية-ثعبان-في-المنام-لابن-سيرين?page=897" > seeing a snake </a> blue dead in a dream, it means that the seer has gotten rid of evil and gotten rid of the enemy and will live a happy life.<br/>If he sees that the blue snake is attacking in a dream, it means that the dreamer is committing many sins and forbidden things, and that the vision warns him to repent from them.</p>
<p>Seeing a large number of blue snakes in the house in a dream indicates the occurrence of family problems between family members.</p>
<p>Seeing blue snake eggs in a dream indicates a strong enemy, and seeing blue snake venom in a dream indicates the discovery of the enemy's plans.<br/>Indicates <a href="https://gptafser.com/post/تفسير-رؤية-ثعبان-في-المنام-لابن-سيرين?page=897" > seeing a snake </a> blue small in a dream to form a strong family and the birth of strong children.</p><div class="angwp_84394 _ning_cont _ning_hidden _ning_outer _align_center responsive" data-aid="0" data-bid="84394" data-size="custom" style="max-width:100%; width:100%;height:inherit;"><div class="_ning_label _left" style=""></div><div class="_ning_inner" style=""><script type="text/javascript">
