<p>Dream interpretation according to the Arabic alphabet from Imam Ja'far al-Sadiq's book, from the letter Alif to the letter Ya, all letters, and according to the Shia sect and others.</p>
<p><span></span></p>
<p>Search for the letter that your dream begins with, then search for your dream within it (for example, search for the letter Ba, then search for the interpretation of the section in it).</p>
<h2><span>The letter Alif or the Hamza (A)</span></h2>
<p>Seeing Ibrahim (peace be upon him) indicates pilgrimage, the birth of righteous children, and warns of safety from hardships and disasters.<br/>Seeing the needle: It warns of marriage for the unmarried, covering and money for the poor and needy, and breaking the needle is separation and corruption.<br/>Seeing the jug: It indicates the repentance of the sinner, <a href="https://gptafser.com/post/تفسير-حلم-ولادة-طفل-في-المنام?page=943" >the birth of a child</a> a male in the dream of a <a href="https://gptafser.com/post/تفسير-حلم-المرأة-الحامل-لابن-سيرين?page=691" >pregnant woman</a>, and it is a symbol of laughter, joy, and play.<br/>Seeing Iblis: It symbolizes innovation, temptation, committing sins, cunning, deception, division, consuming interest, and forbidden money.<br/><a href="https://gptafser.com/post/تفسير-رؤية-الكمثرى-في-المنام?page=554" >Seeing the pear</a>: In its time, it symbolizes sustenance and kindness, the return of the traveler and the absent, the departure of worries, sickness, and evil, and <a href="https://gptafser.com/post/تفسير-رؤية-المريض-في-المنام?page=3431" >seeing the sick person</a> eating the pear indicates healing.<br/>Looking at holy places: Good tidings of marriage for the unmarried, divorce for the married, and staying away from sins, disobedience, and enmity.<br/>Crowds of people: It indicates spoiled goods, transgressions, and corrupt values, or house theft.<br/><a href="https://gptafser.com/post/تفسير-حلم-رؤية-الأخ-في-المنام-لابن-سيرين?page=544" >Seeing the brother</a>: It symbolizes cooperation in money, trade, or work.<br/>Performing the testimony: It symbolizes paying debts and abandoning covenants. Keeping the testimony symbolizes greed and hatred, and it can symbolize illness.<br/><a href="https://gptafser.com/post/تفسير-حلم-رؤية-الأذان-في-المنام?page=3925" >Seeing the call to prayer</a>: It indicates pilgrimage, or it may symbolize gossip or being accused of theft, or it may be an indication of elevation and reputation.<br/>The ear: The large ear indicates guidance, acceptance, and satisfaction.<br/>The purple color: It symbolizes the pure or wealthy woman who speaks a lot and her relatives.<br/>The cradle: It indicates corruption, if the dreamer rocks it.<br/>Rice: It symbolizes money and profit.<br/>The earth: It indicates keeping secrets and safety from fears and dangers, and seeing agricultural lands symbolizes agriculture and fertility, and an eclipse indicates loss and neglect, and vast land is travel.<br/>The rabbit: It symbolizes the cowardly man or the cowardly woman, and slaughtering the rabbit indicates the permanent and impermanent husband.<br/>Izar: It symbolizes the free woman, and the red mark symbolizes the accusation of doubt.<br/>Hearing: It symbolizes gossip, lies, and breaking oaths.<br/>The lion: It symbolizes injustice or death, and seeing the lion's mate (the lioness) indicates the evil woman.<br/>Speed: It symbolizes the speed of worship and kindness, and it warns the sick of death.<br/>The cylinder: It symbolizes the house and the servant if it is made of wood or clay.<br/>The name: Seeing it with her is a good omen and worthy of praise, if a person sees that he changed his name to another name.<br/>The finger: It symbolizes help and assistance from relatives, children, sustenance, and money.<br/>The sacrifice: It symbolizes sacrifice, faith, truthfulness, money for the poor, and safety from fear.<br/>Borrowing: Borrowing or lending something symbolizes love and kindness, or hatred and conflict that does not last.<br/>Itikaf: It symbolizes good deeds if it is in the mosque.<br/>Bankruptcy: It symbolizes lack of debts.<br/>Food: Eating under the lights symbolizes destruction, eating among people symbolizes lust, and <a href="https://gptafser.com/post/تفسير-رؤية-اللحم-في-المنام-لابن-سيرين-والنابلسي?page=676" >seeing meat</a> eaten symbolizes evil.<br/>The mother: The state of the mother in the dream symbolizes the state of the dreamer and may indicate comfort.<br/>Canceling harm: It symbolizes jealousy for religion, husband, children, or many charities, or seeking forgiveness for sins.<br/>In front of prayer: It symbolizes the reason for the matter, and praying with people in a direction other than the qibla symbolizes betrayal and innovation.<br/>Annunciation: It means repentance and relief.<br/>The nose: It means winning over with money or children.<br/>Contraction: It can symbolize money or sins and transgressions.<br/>Disturbance: It symbolizes loss.<br/>Goose: It symbolizes women with money and beauty.<br/>The pyramids: They symbolize living with strangers, or they indicate longevity.<br/>Gazelles: Dignity and victory over enemies.<br/>Verses of the Quran: Verses of mercy are verses of mercy, and verses of punishment symbolize the punishment of God Almighty.</p>
