<div>
<p>A dream about being drunk indicates that you will show indifference to what is happening around you, and other interpretations that we mention about a single woman and a single man, married, pregnant and divorced, such as <a href="https://gptafser.com/post/تفسير-رؤية-الأخ-في-المنام-لابن-سيرين?page=544" > seeing a brother</a> drunk. Or a husband, or a drunk lover, or a drunk father, or I dreamed of being drunk or drunk chasing me, and a dead man <a href="https://gptafser.com/post/تفسير-حلم-شرب-الخمر-في-المنام?page=566" > drinking wine</a> for great Arab dream interpreters, such as <a href="https://gptafser.com/post/تفسير-حلم-ابن-سيرين-في-المنام?page=1665" > Ibn Sirin</a> and others, continuing the topic:</p>
<p><span></span></p>
<p>Seeing a <strong>drunkard in a dream</strong> is among the different and frightening dreams that we see in dreams, which carry many important signs to reach the dreamer, as wine is among the prohibited drinks in all heavenly religions, which is what God and His Messenger prohibited in the Quran. And Sunnah, and let us Messenger of Allah, may God bless him and grant him peace, not drink it because it robs the mind, makes a person ignorant of all his actions, and therefore causes many problems for those around him.</p>
<p>After that, we will examine for you the interpretation of seeing a drunkard in a dream, as explained by Imam <a href="https://gptafser.com/post/تفسير-حلم-ابن-سيرين-في-المنام?page=1665" > Ibn Sirin</a>:</p><div class="angwp_84394 _ning_cont _ning_hidden _ning_outer _align_center responsive" data-aid="0" data-bid="84394" data-size="custom" style="max-width:100%; width:100%;height:inherit;"><div class="_ning_label _left" style=""></div><div class="_ning_inner" style=""><script type="text/javascript">
