<p><span></span></p>
<h2><span>Interpretation of a drunk person in a dream</span></h2>
<p>Seeing <a href="https://gptafser.com/post/تفسير-حلم-شخص-ما-في-المنام?page=2395" > someone</a> drunk in a dream means that there will be positive changes in your life in matters that you did not expect to happen<br/>And seeing a person in a state of intoxication in a dream is evidence of kindness, if the dreamer feels that he is in a state of tension and sadness because he <a href="https://gptafser.com/post/تفسير-حلم-شرب-الخمر-في-المنام?page=566" > drank wine</a> and got drunk.</p>
<p>Seeing a faithful <a href="https://gptafser.com/post/تفسير-رؤية-شخص-في-المنام?page=1714" > person</a> drunk in a dream is evidence of his good coming in all matters of life.<br/>As it is indicated by <strong>drinking alcohol in a dream</strong> about the good earnings of a man in the case of the nectar of his heart and his refinement.<br/>Seeing <a href="https://gptafser.com/post/تفسير-رؤية-الخمر-في-المنام-لابن-سيرين-والنابلسي?page=648" > wine</a> in a dream means that money and blessings will come to the seer without any effort.<br/>And it indicates intoxication in a dream with accompanying people with positions and money.</p>
<p>Seeing a religious person drunk in a dream is evidence of his great love for God and His Messenger.<br/>And the merchant who trades in <a href="https://gptafser.com/post/تفسير-حلم-شرب-الخمر-في-المنام?page=566" > wine</a> that is permissible in a dream is evidence of acquiring livelihood, blessing and money in the near future.<br/>Seeing a scholar drunk in a dream is evidence of a great increase in his knowledge.<br/>Seeing <strong>a sick person drunk in a dream</strong> is evidence of the details of the treatment of the disease.<br/>Drinking grape wine is a sign of good, blessing, and money coming to the dreamer.<br/>Pressing wine in a dream is evidence of a person serving the king or sultan in the near future.</p><div class="angwp_84394 _ning_cont _ning_hidden _ning_outer _align_center responsive" data-aid="0" data-bid="84394" data-size="custom" style="max-width:100%; width:100%;height:inherit;"><div class="_ning_label _left" style=""></div><div class="_ning_inner" style=""><script type="text/javascript">
