</script></div></div><div class="clear"></div>
<p><span></span></p>
<p>For the dreamer to see himself drunk from wine and tearing his clothes is evidence that he is a person who longs for blessings.<br/>Seeing a merchant drunk from drinking alcohol in a dream is evidence of the unlawful money he will get.<br/>As for the evildoer, he <a href="https://gptafser.com/post/تفسير-حلم-شرب-الخمر-في-المنام?page=566" > drinks wine</a> and drinks in a dream, then this is evidence of theft and great bribery that he will give.<br/>Seeing him in a dream that he is drunk without drinking alcohol is evidence of fear and anxiety in the person's life about the future.<br/>Seeing a dreamer drunk from <a href="https://gptafser.com/post/تفسير-حلم-شرب-الخمر-في-المنام?page=566" > drinking wine</a> in a dream is evidence that you are approaching the people of the offices in a forbidden way.<br/>Intoxication in a dream is evidence of ignorance in the dreamer's life.</p>
<p>Whoever knows <strong>the dead drunk in a dream</strong> and this indicates that the dead is in comfort and pleasure in the hereafter, then <a href="https://gptafser.com/post/تفسير-حلم-شرب-الخمر-في-المنام?page=566" > drinking wine</a> from the people of Paradise, otherwise he died and he intended to do that, or he was in his worldly life for those who considered it permissible.</p>
<p>Intoxication in a dream also indicates great cunning and hypocrisy around the dreamer, so he must be careful.</p><div class="angwp_84394 _ning_cont _ning_hidden _ning_outer _align_center responsive" data-aid="0" data-bid="84394" data-size="custom" style="max-width:100%; width:100%;height:inherit;"><div class="_ning_label _left" style=""></div><div class="_ning_inner" style=""><script type="text/javascript">
