<p><span></span></p>
<p>Whoever sees her? <strong>The father is drunk in a dream</strong> and this indicates good and acquiring authority, and <a href="https://gptafser.com/post/تفسير-حلم-الكثير-من-المال-لابن-سيرين?page=1849" > a lot of money</a>, and abundance of sustenance for this father and his family.<br/>Seeing <strong>my brother is drunk in a dream</strong> is evidence that this brother will receive a lot of benefit and a lot of sustenance in the hereafter.<br/>As you see <strong>the lover is drunk in a dream</strong>, it is a sign of fear and awe of God Almighty<br/>A dream about <strong>the husband is drunk in a dream</strong> is a sign of the emergence of a problem that will lead to a great competition that will appear to him with a strong person.</p>
<p><a href="https://gptafser.com/post/تفسير-حلم-شرب-الخمر-في-المنام?page=566" > Drinking wine</a> in a dream is evidence of the unlawful money that the person will gain unlawfully.<br/>As for <a href="https://gptafser.com/post/تفسير-حلم-شرب-الخمر-في-المنام?page=566" > drinking wine</a> after a quarrel in a dream, it is evidence of the disputes that a person is exposed to.<br/>Drinking <a href="https://gptafser.com/post/تفسير-حلم-شرب-الخمر-في-المنام?page=566" > wine</a> in a dream is evidence of the great sins that a person will commit.<br/><a href="https://gptafser.com/post/تفسير-رؤية-الخمر-في-المنام-لابن-سيرين-والنابلسي?page=648" > Seeing wine</a> without eating it in a dream is evidence of temptation, sin, and gossip that spreads in the place.<br/>Also, seeing alcohol without consuming it is evidence of lying and hypocrisy.<br/>Seeing a sinner <a href="https://gptafser.com/post/تفسير-حلم-شرب-الخمر-في-المنام?page=566" > drinking wine</a> in a dream is evidence of committing major sins.<br/>Wine in a dream is evidence of the presence of a bad woman in the dreamer's life, you should be careful.</p>
<h2><span>Interpretation of a dream about a drunkard</span></h2>
<p>If you are drunk in a dream, this warns that your cheerful nature will make you ignore life's worries. If you see others drunk, it indicates that you are not interested in the behavior and actions of your companions.</p><div class="angwp_84394 _ning_cont _ning_hidden _ning_outer _align_center responsive" data-aid="0" data-bid="84394" data-size="custom" style="max-width:100%; width:100%;height:inherit;"><div class="_ning_label _left" style=""></div><div class="_ning_inner" style=""><script type="text/javascript">
