<p><span></span></p>
<p>Seeing <strong><a href="https://gptafser.com/post/تفسير-حلم-شرب-الخمر-في-المنام?page=566" > drinking wine</a> in a dream</strong> refers to unlawful money and its profits, and it is without hardship or the least effort, and it has been said that drinking alcohol without a contestant or rival who drinks it indicates unlawful money, and a dispute between another person and the seer indicates drinking alcohol in a dream for lawful money that others compete with, and the amount of competition for money corresponds to the amount of competition and dispute between the fortuneteller and this person about <a href="https://gptafser.com/post/تفسير-حلم-شرب-الخمر-في-المنام?page=566" > drinking wine</a> in a dream</p>
<p>As for Al-Nabulsi, he did not differ much in his opinion from what <a href="https://gptafser.com/post/تفسير-حلم-ابن-سيرين-في-المنام?page=1665" > Ibn Sirin</a> said, as he said that wine in a dream is forbidden money, and drinking it may indicate a sin or a great sin, or a great and wide livelihood, based on the state of the dreamer's piety and his closeness or distance from God Almighty, and <a href="https://gptafser.com/post/تفسير-حلم-شرب-الخمر-في-المنام?page=566" > drinking wine</a> is forbidden money without dispute, and drinking it in the presence of a competitor symbolizes competition and a lot of talk.</p>
<p>As for Ibn Shaheen, he did not add to the words and interpretation of <a href="https://gptafser.com/post/تفسير-حلم-ابن-سيرين-في-المنام?page=1665" > Ibn Sirin</a> and Al-Nabulsi, except that he said that seeing the dreamer in <a href="https://gptafser.com/post/تفسير-حلم-شرب-الخمر-في-المنام?page=566" > drinking wine</a> until he drinks from it and loses his balance indicates that he took forbidden money.  Stressing this, and it is not required that forbidden money is only dubious money, but stolen money or the confiscation of an orphan's money is forbidden money.</p><div class="angwp_84394 _ning_cont _ning_hidden _ning_outer _align_center responsive" data-aid="0" data-bid="84394" data-size="custom" style="max-width:100%; width:100%;height:inherit;"><div class="_ning_label _left" style=""></div><div class="_ning_inner" style=""><script type="text/javascript">
