<p><span></span></p>
<p>And intoxication in a dream symbolizes great ignorance, and <a href="https://gptafser.com/post/تفسير-رؤية-السكر-في-المنام?page=3687" > seeing intoxication</a> in a dream for someone who is afraid of something is a good thing, and seeing a person in his dream as if he is claiming to be drunk while he is not drunk and not drunk. The drinker says that he betrays and claims that he can do something when he cannot do it at all.  .</p>
<p>It may also indicate that he has suffered a calamity that reverses him and removes his mind until he gets drunk and does not <a href="https://gptafser.com/post/تفسير-حلم-شرب-الخمر-في-المنام?page=566" > drink wine</a>, while if the seer is among the righteous and sees himself in a dream conquering him. Intoxication, then this indicates that his heart is full of love for God Almighty...</p>
